node.text:
#ad I’ve been stressing about my breakouts recently but @Burtsbees got my back! Like everyone else, I’ve been using them for YEARS. Their Natural Acne Solutions is AMAZING!

 

The Purifying Gel Cleanser works on acne and prevents future breakouts without over drying. It has Cica to soothe skin and the consistency is amazing!

 

The Clarifying Toner helps eliminate excess oil and it has Salicylic Acid to penetrate clogged pores. I feel like a lot of people skip toners so it's definitely the most slept on skincare step.

 

The Targeted Spot Treatment helps reduce redness and size of breakouts and honestly it just gives me peace of mind in case I have a giant pimple that needs some work lol. 

 

The best part is that all of the products from this acne collection have Cica to soothe skin and Salicylic Acid to penetrate clogged pores! #noanimaltesting
